	- converted to correct type pivot vector element in pixmap rotation.

2019-01-28 cage

	* src/nodgui-mw.lisp:

	- sort is destructive, copy list to prevent problems.
	- fixed indentation.

2019-01-26 cage

	* src/canvas.lisp,
	* src/demo-tests.lisp,
	* src/event-parser.lisp,
	* src/event-symbols.lisp,
